data.description: Sitting on a private street, you are sure to fall in love with this townhome! On the first floor you will find an updated kitchen with granite countertops, beautiful backsplash, a kitchen island and a 1 year old refrigerator that will stay with the property. The living room is ample size with a beautiful fireplace and windows that look out onto the patio. For your convenience, there is a half bath that sits right off the kitchen. Upstairs, the main bedroom sports a tiled walk in shower that will surely win you over and don't miss the private balcony that overlooks your patio below! Each bedroom also has spacious closets. You enter your 2 car garage from the private drive in the back of your townhome and one of the best features is your golf course view from your backyard!
